{"tid":887650,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"新港式文字溝通system (粤語)","createTime":"2018-11-03T05:41:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-03T05:51:52.000Z","uid":115880,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"c446f28765f804488c3ce3707ddcc21175945c00","tid":887650,"uid":115880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:41:03.000Z","msg":"香港長期受支囯文化入滲<br />\n仲有D支囯人扮港人既打手<br />\n我覺得有必要硏究一套獨有既文字溝通系統<br />\n用來分開D支囯人<br />\n<br />\n我既睇法係 中文書面語保留<br />\n但日常文字溝通用新系統 例如玩討論區 watsapp<br />\n希望可以一齊度下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n希望可以整合一套粤語人容易上手溝通system<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e0f48643fe10a07d129439c5ac0f794fe551860","tid":887650,"uid":115880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:43:54.000Z","msg":"希望各位師兄 年輕人俾下意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a96e97c68d4175f411a497653c0eb1475c98155","tid":887650,"uid":105678,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:46:48.000Z","msg":"倉頡頭尾碼，速成碼<br />\n<br />\n又好似太複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d17f3acbff5335f7a3c5ffcf461f0b8011ae012","tid":887650,"uid":115880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-03T05:51:52.000Z","msg":"可唔可以好似日本咁 分開口語同詞語？"}]}